==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flooding
<hw>Flood"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The filling or covering with
water or other fluid; overflow; inundation; the filling anything to
excess.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An abnormal or excessive discharge
of blood from the uterus.</def> <rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>floodlit</ent>⟦br⟧
